StarFlier slept in dragon mode.  Her power cells recharged as they 
always did when she slept.  She awoke to the sound of the alarm going 
off from her trip lazars.  She jumped and looked around.  She saw a 
large animal. It was about 6 and a half feet tall. Massive branch 
like things sticking out of it's large elongated head.  It's legs 
were very long and very thin. It had dark brown skin and fur.  What 
she saw was a moose, but since she had never seen one before, it 
looked like a monster. It was larger than her, but she knew she could 
take on anything she had seen so far in the woods.  She reset her 
little alarm system and laid back down and went to sleep.
